data.description: Settle into the comfort of this 1478-SF stucco townhouse on 2409 square feet in McAllen. This welcoming floor plan delivers 2 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, living room with hardwood floors, tasteful dining room, master suite with walk-in closet for your wardrobe, dual sinks, stylish kitchen with electric range, microwave, breakfast bar for on-the-go meals, granite countertops, barrel tile roof, off-street parking, mature plants, gated community. This townhouse is conveniently located to major shopping, restaurants, and the 2nd Street walking trails!
